# Binary
dnshealth_exporter
*.exe
*.test
*.out
# Cross-compiled / platform-suffixed binaries (e.g.,
# dnshealth_exporter_linux_arm64). Anchored to repo root so a future
# Go file named dnshealth_exporter_*.go in any sub-package wouldn't
# get accidentally ignored.
/dnshealth_exporter_*
# Stray binary produced if someone runs `go build ./demo/dashboard`
# instead of the documented `make dashboards` / `go run`. Rooted so it
# does not also ignore the demo/dashboard/ source directory.
/dashboard

# GoReleaser
dist/


# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Demo local overrides (port etc.)
demo/.env
/demo/dashboard/dashboard
